Name and contact information for the trial sponsor {5b}The University of Birmingham is the trial sponsor. Contact: University of Birmingham, Edgbaston, Birmingham, B15 2TT; researchgovernance@bham.ac.uk.
Role of sponsor {5c}Besides providing peer review advice at the time of funding, the funder and sponsor played no role in the design of the study, in collection, analysis, and interpretation of data or in writing this manuscript.
